Notes: Nicole Dierking goes the length of the floor for a layup with 17 seconds left
to give UMR the win...UMSL's Courtney Watts missed a runner just before the
buzzer...With the win, UMR clinches a berth to the GLVC Tournament next week
in Evansville, Ind....UMR will play at Southern Indiana Thursday (5:15 p.m.).
